---
// Curiosity — Easter egg page, completamente autónoma con tema matrix/hacker
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>// ACCESO CONCEDIDO — Archivo Clasificado</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=VT323&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Mono:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 32 32'%3E%3Crect width='32' height='32' rx='7' fill='%23050912'/%3E%3Ctext x='3' y='23' font-family='monospace' font-weight='bold' font-size='19' fill='%2300ff88'%3EDM%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg: #050912;
            --green: #00ff88;
            --green-dim: rgba(0,255,136,0.08);
            --green-border: rgba(0,255,136,0.2);
            --red: #ff3355;
            --red-dim: rgba(255,51,85,0.08);
            --cyan: #06b6d4;
            --purple: #a855f7;
            --text: #e2e8f0;
            --muted: #64748b;
            --muted2: #475569;
            --gold: #f59e0b;
            --surface: rgba(15,20,40,0.7);
        }

        *, *::before, *::after { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }
        html { scroll-behavior:smooth; }
        body {
            background:var(--bg);
            color:var(--text);
            font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;
            overflow-x:hidden;
            cursor:crosshair;
        }

        /* NOISE TEXTURE */
        body::before {
            content:'';
            position:fixed;inset:0;pointer-events:none;z-index:9997;
            background-image:url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 200 200' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)' opacity='0.03'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
            background-size:200px;
            opacity:.4;
        }
        /* SCAN LINES */
        body::after {
            content:'';
            position:fixed;inset:0;pointer-events:none;z-index:9998;
            background:repeating-linear-gradient(
                0deg,
                transparent,
                transparent 3px,
                rgba(0,255,136,.009) 3px,
                rgba(0,255,136,.009) 4px
            );
        }

        #matrix-canvas { position:fixed;inset:0;opacity:.055;pointer-events:none;z-index:0; }

        /* CLASSIFIED WATERMARK */
        .classified-bg {
            position:fixed;top:50%;left:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%) rotate(-35deg);
            font-family:'VT323',monospace;font-size:clamp(5rem,15vw,11rem);
            color:rgba(255,51,85,.028);letter-spacing:8px;pointer-events:none;
            z-index:0;white-space:nowrap;user-select:none;
        }

        /* BACK BTN */
        .back-btn {
            position:fixed;top:24px;left:24px;z-index:10000;
            display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:9px 18px;
            background:rgba(5,9,18,.95);border:1px solid var(--green-border);
            border-radius:4px;color:var(--green);text-decoration:none;
            font-size:.72rem;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;
            transition:all .25s;backdrop-filter:blur(12px);
        }
        .back-btn:hover { background:var(--green-dim);box-shadow:0 0 24px rgba(0,255,136,.18); }

        /* ACHIEVEMENT */
        .achievement {
            position:fixed;top:24px;right:24px;z-index:10000;
            background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(5,9,18,.98),rgba(20,25,50,.98));
            border:1px solid var(--gold);border-radius:10px;padding:14px 18px;
            display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;max-width:320px;
            box-shadow:0 8px 40px rgba(245,158,11,.25),inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.05);
            transform:translateX(420px);opacity:0;
            transition:all .55s cubic-bezier(.34,1.56,.64,1);
        }
        .achievement.show { transform:translateX(0);opacity:1; }
        .ach-icon {
            width:46px;height:46px;border-radius:9px;
            background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--gold),#fbbf24);
            display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
            font-size:1.4rem;flex-shrink:0;
            animation:achSpin .5s cubic-bezier(.34,1.56,.64,1) .4s both;
        }
        @keyframes achSpin { from{transform:rotate(-180deg) scale(0)} to{transform:rotate(0) scale(1)} }
        .ach-text { display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:3px; }
        .ach-label { font-size:.58rem;color:var(--gold);letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:700; }
        .ach-title { font-size:.88rem;color:var(--text);font-weight:700; }
        .ach-desc { font-size:.68rem;color:var(--muted); }

        /* WRAP */
        .wrap { position:relative;z-index:1;max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;padding:110px 40px 80px; }

        /* ── HEADER ── */
        .glitch-header { text-align:center;margin-bottom:80px; }
        .status-bar {
            display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;
            font-size:.64rem;letter-spacing:4px;text-transform:uppercase;
            color:var(--green);margin-bottom:32px;padding:7px 18px;
            border:1px solid var(--green-border);border-radius:3px;
            background:var(--green-dim);
            animation:statusBlink 2.5s step-end infinite;
        }
        @keyframes statusBlink { 0%,100%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:.55} }
        .sdot { width:7px;height:7px;background:var(--green);border-radius:50%;animation:sdotPulse 1.2s ease-in-out infinite; }
        @keyframes sdotPulse { 0%,100%{opacity:1;transform:scale(1)} 50%{opacity:.3;transform:scale(1.4)} }

        .main-title {
            font-family:'VT323',monospace;
            font-size:clamp(3rem,11vw,7.5rem);color:var(--green);
            letter-spacing:6px;text-transform:uppercase;line-height:.88;margin-bottom:14px;
            text-shadow:0 0 50px rgba(0,255,136,.45),0 0 100px rgba(0,255,136,.15);
            animation:glitch 5s infinite;
        }
        @keyframes glitch {
            0%,88%,100% { clip-path:none;transform:translate(0);color:var(--green); }
            90% { clip-path:inset(18% 0 58% 0);transform:translate(-5px,0);color:var(--red); }
            92% { clip-path:inset(55% 0 8% 0);transform:translate(5px,0);color:var(--cyan); }
            94% { clip-path:none;transform:translate(0);color:var(--green); }
        }
        .main-subtitle { font-size:.78rem;color:var(--muted);letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-top:14px; }
        .stamp {
            display:inline-block;border:3px solid var(--red);color:var(--red);
            font-family:'VT323',monospace;font-size:1.6rem;letter-spacing:5px;
            padding:4px 18px;border-radius:3px;transform:rotate(-7deg);opacity:.65;margin-top:20px;
            text-shadow:0 0 14px rgba(255,51,85,.5);
            box-shadow:0 0 20px rgba(255,51,85,.12),inset 0 0 20px rgba(255,51,85,.04);
        }

        /* ── SECTION SEPARATOR ── */
        .sep {
            display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px;margin:0 0 50px;
        }
        .sep-badge {
            font-size:.58rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;
            padding:4px 12px;border-radius:3px;flex-shrink:0;
        }
        .sep-badge.red { background:var(--red-dim);border:1px solid rgba(255,51,85,.3);color:var(--red); }
        .sep-badge.cyan { background:rgba(6,182,212,.08);border:1px solid rgba(6,182,212,.25);color:var(--cyan); }
        .sep-badge.purple { background:rgba(168,85,247,.08);border:1px solid rgba(168,85,247,.25);color:var(--purple); }
        .sep-title { font-family:'VT323',monospace;font-size:1.7rem;color:var(--text);letter-spacing:2px; }
        .sep-line { flex:1;height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(100,116,139,.3),transparent); }

        /* ── QUOTE ── */
        .quote-section {
            background:var(--green-dim);
            border:1px solid var(--green-border);border-left:3px solid var(--green);
            border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:34px 40px 30px;
            margin-bottom:70px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;
        }
        .quote-section::before {
            content:'"';position:absolute;top:-24px;left:16px;
            font-family:'VT323',monospace;font-size:7rem;color:var(--green);opacity:.12;line-height:1;
            pointer-events:none;
        }
        .quote-section::after {
            content:'';position:absolute;top:0;right:0;width:80px;height:100%;
            background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,rgba(0,255,136,.03));pointer-events:none;
        }
        .qt { font-family:'VT323',monospace;font-size:1.95rem;color:var(--green);letter-spacing:1px;line-height:1.3;margin-bottom:16px; }
        .qa { font-size:.71rem;color:var(--muted2);letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase; }

        /* ── DOSSIER CARDS ── */
        .d-grid { display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:18px;margin-bottom:70px; }
        .d-card {
            background:var(--surface);
            border:1px solid rgba(100,116,139,.15);
            border-radius:8px;padding:28px 26px 22px;
            transition:border-color .25s,box-shadow .25s,transform .25s;
            position:relative;overflow:hidden;
        }
        .d-card::before {
            content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:2px;
            opacity:0;transition:opacity .25s;
        }
        .d-card:nth-child(1)::before { background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--green),transparent); }
        .d-card:nth-child(2)::before { background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--gold),transparent); }
        .d-card:nth-child(3)::before { background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--cyan),transparent); }
        .d-card:nth-child(4)::before { background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--red),transparent); }
        .d-card:hover::before { opacity:1; }
        .d-card:hover {
            border-color:rgba(100,116,139,.3);
            box-shadow:0 4px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.4);
            transform:translateY(-3px);
        }
        .d-card-num {
            position:absolute;top:12px;right:16px;
            font-family:'VT323',monospace;font-size:3.5rem;color:rgba(100,116,139,.08);
            line-height:1;pointer-events:none;user-select:none;
        }
        .ci { font-size:1.9rem;margin-bottom:14px;display:block; }
        .cl { font-size:.58rem;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted2);margin-bottom:7px; }
        .ct { font-family:'VT323',monospace;font-size:1.45rem;color:var(--green);margin-bottom:10px;letter-spacing:1px; }
        .cp { font-size:.77rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.75; }
        .tag {
            display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;font-size:.6rem;
            letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;padding:3px 10px;
            border-radius:3px;margin-top:14px;font-weight:700;
        }
        .tg { background:var(--green-dim);border:1px solid var(--green-border);color:var(--green); }
        .tr { background:var(--red-dim);border:1px solid rgba(255,51,85,.28);color:var(--red); }
        .to { background:rgba(245,158,11,.08);border:1px solid rgba(245,158,11,.28);color:var(--gold); }

        /* ── STATS ── */
        .stats-row {
            display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);
            border:1px solid var(--green-border);border-radius:8px;
            overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:70px;
            background:rgba(0,255,136,.025);
        }
        .si {
            text-align:center;padding:24px 12px;position:relative;
        }
        .si:not(:last-child)::after {
            content:'';position:absolute;right:0;top:20%;height:60%;width:1px;
            background:rgba(100,116,139,.2);
        }
        .sn {
            font-family:'VT323',monospace;font-size:2.8rem;color:var(--green);
            line-height:1;text-shadow:0 0 20px rgba(0,255,136,.4);
        }
        .sl { font-size:.58rem;color:var(--muted);letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-top:6px;line-height:1.5; }

        /* ── TERMINAL ── */
        .term-wrap { margin-bottom:70px; }
        .term-bar {
            display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:rgba(22,26,42,.95);
            padding:10px 16px;border-radius:8px 8px 0 0;
            border:1px solid rgba(100,116,139,.18);border-bottom:none;
        }
        .tdot { width:12px;height:12px;border-radius:50%; }
        .tc{background:#ff5f57}.tm{background:#ffbd2e}.tx{background:#28ca41}
        .ttitle { font-size:.68rem;color:var(--muted);margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px; }
        .ttitle-path { color:var(--green);opacity:.6; }
        .terminal {
            background:rgba(4,7,16,.98);border:1px solid rgba(100,116,139,.18);border-top:none;
            border-radius:0 0 8px 8px;padding:22px;min-height:250px;
            font-size:.78rem;line-height:1.9;overflow-y:auto;max-height:360px;
        }
        .tl { display:flex;gap:8px;margin-bottom:4px; }
        .tp { color:var(--green);flex-shrink:0; }
        .tk { color:var(--cyan); }
        .to2 { margin-left:14px;margin-bottom:2px; }
        .to2.g{color:var(--green)}.to2.m{color:var(--muted)}.to2.o{color:var(--gold)}.to2.r{color:var(--red)}
        .tcursor {
            display:inline-block;width:8px;height:14px;background:var(--green);
            animation:tcBlink 1s step-end infinite;vertical-align:middle;margin-left:2px;
        }
        @keyframes tcBlink { 0%,100%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:0} }

        /* ── FUN FACTS ── */
        .facts-wrap { margin-bottom:70px; }
        .fi {
            display:grid;grid-template-columns:28px 1fr;align-items:start;gap:14px;
            padding:14px 18px;border-radius:6px;margin-bottom:6px;
            background:rgba(15,20,40,.4);
            border:1px solid transparent;
            transition:border-color .2s,background .2s;
            font-size:.78rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.7;
        }
        .fi:hover { border-color:rgba(6,182,212,.2);background:rgba(6,182,212,.03);color:var(--text); }
        .fi-num {
            font-family:'VT323',monospace;font-size:1.2rem;color:var(--cyan);
            opacity:.5;line-height:1.4;text-align:right;
        }

        /* ── CV ── */
        .cv-section {
            background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(168,85,247,.06),rgba(6,182,212,.06));
            border:1px solid rgba(168,85,247,.22);border-radius:8px;
            padding:36px;text-align:center;margin-bottom:70px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;
        }
        .cv-section::before {
            content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;
            background:radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 0%,rgba(168,85,247,.08),transparent 70%);
            pointer-events:none;
        }
        .cv-section h3 {
            font-family:'VT323',monospace;font-size:1.8rem;color:var(--purple);
            letter-spacing:3px;margin-bottom:10px;
        }
        .cv-section p { font-size:.77rem;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:28px; }
        .cv-btns { display:flex;gap:14px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap; }
        .cvb {
            display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;padding:12px 26px;border-radius:6px;
            text-decoration:none;font-size:.74rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1.5px;
            text-transform:uppercase;transition:all .25s;cursor:pointer;
            border:none;font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;
        }
        .cvb-es { background:var(--purple);color:#fff; }
        .cvb-es:hover { background:#9333ea;transform:translateY(-3px);box-shadow:0 10px 28px rgba(168,85,247,.38); }
        .cvb-en { background:transparent;color:var(--cyan);border:2px solid var(--cyan); }
        .cvb-en:hover { background:rgba(6,182,212,.1);transform:translateY(-3px);box-shadow:0 10px 28px rgba(6,182,212,.12); }

        /* ── BACK TO REALITY ── */
        .back-r { text-align:center;padding:50px 20px;border-top:1px solid rgba(100,116,139,.12); }
        .back-r p { font-size:.72rem;color:var(--muted2);letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:28px; }
        .btn-r {
            display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:13px 32px;
            background:transparent;border:1px solid rgba(0,255,136,.28);border-radius:4px;
            color:var(--green);font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:.76rem;
            letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;text-decoration:none;transition:all .25s;
        }
        .btn-r:hover { background:var(--green-dim);box-shadow:0 0 32px rgba(0,255,136,.12);transform:translateY(-2px); }

        @media(max-width:768px) {
            .wrap { padding:90px 20px 60px; }
            .d-grid { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
            .stats-row { grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr); }
            .achievement { right:12px;max-width:calc(100vw - 24px); }
            .main-title { font-size:3.2rem; }
            .cv-btns { flex-direction:column;align-items:center; }
            .quote-section { padding:26px 24px 22px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<canvas id="matrix-canvas"></canvas>
<div class="classified-bg" id="classified-bg">CLASIFICADO</div>

<a href="/" class="back-btn" id="back-top-btn">
    <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i>
    <span data-i18n="back_btn">Salir</span>
</a>

<div class="achievement" id="achievement">
    <div class="ach-icon">🏆</div>
    <div class="ach-text">
        <span class="ach-label" data-i18n="ach_label">Logro desbloqueado</span>
        <span class="ach-title" data-i18n="ach_title">La Curiosidad</span>
        <span class="ach-desc" data-i18n="ach_desc">Encontraste el archivo clasificado</span>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="wrap">

    <!-- HEADER -->
    <div class="glitch-header">
        <div class="status-bar">
            <span class="sdot"></span>
            <span data-i18n="status_bar">CONEXIÓN SEGURA ESTABLECIDA</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="main-title" data-i18n="main_title">ACCESO<br>CONCEDIDO</h1>
        <p class="main-subtitle" data-i18n="main_subtitle">// Archivo personal de Darío Martínez — CONFIDENCIAL</p>
        <div class="stamp" data-i18n="stamp">CLASIFICADO</div>
    </div>

    <!-- QUOTE -->
    <div class="quote-section">
        <p class="qt" data-i18n="quote_text">"La curiosidad mató al gato... pero la satisfacción lo resucitó."</p>
        <p class="qa" data-i18n="quote_attr">— Los perros, probablemente · Y también un desarrollador que se quedó depurando hasta las 2am</p>
    </div>

    <!-- DOSSIER -->
    <div class="sep">
        <span class="sep-badge red" data-i18n="dossier_badge">CLASSIFIED</span>
        <span class="sep-title" data-i18n="dossier_title">DOSSIER PERSONAL</span>
        <div class="sep-line"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="d-grid">
        <div class="d-card">
            <div class="d-card-num">01</div>
            <span class="ci">⚽</span>
            <div class="cl" data-i18n="card1_label">Actividad verificada</div>
            <div class="ct" data-i18n="card1_title">Árbitro de Fútbol</div>
            <p class="cp" data-i18n="card1_text">Árbitro federado en activo. En el campo aprende que hay decisiones difíciles que tomar con seguridad, exactamente como en una code review.</p>
            <span class="tag tg"><i class="fas fa-check"></i> <span data-i18n="card1_tag">FEDERADO</span></span>
        </div>
        <div class="d-card">
            <div class="d-card-num">02</div>
            <span class="ci">🚵</span>
            <div class="cl" data-i18n="card2_label">Estado: retirado temporalmente</div>
            <div class="ct" data-i18n="card2_title">Mountain Bike</div>
            <p class="cp" data-i18n="card2_text">Durante muchos años recorrió rutas y senderos de montaña. La montaña enseña que el camino más difícil suele tener las mejores vistas.</p>
            <span class="tag to"><i class="fas fa-trophy"></i> <span data-i18n="card2_tag">VETERANO</span></span>
        </div>
        <div class="d-card">
            <div class="d-card-num">03</div>
            <span class="ci">🐾</span>
            <div class="cl" data-i18n="card3_label">Nivel de afecto: crítico</div>
            <div class="ct" data-i18n="card3_title">Amante de los Animales</div>
            <p class="cp" data-i18n="card3_text">Los animales nunca hacen git blame, nunca piden pull request reviews y siempre están disponibles para el pair programming.</p>
            <span class="tag tg"><span data-i18n="card3_tag">CONFIRMADO</span></span>
        </div>
        <div class="d-card">
            <div class="d-card-num">04</div>
            <span class="ci">💻</span>
            <div class="cl" data-i18n="card4_label">Adicción declarada</div>
            <div class="ct" data-i18n="card4_title">Desarrollador Web</div>
            <p class="cp" data-i18n="card4_text">Escribe código que funciona... en su máquina. Especialista en hacer que el cliente diga "¡Exactamente!" cuando ni él sabía lo que quería.</p>
            <span class="tag tr"><i class="fas fa-fire"></i> <span data-i18n="card4_tag">PASIÓN MÁXIMA</span></span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- STATS -->
    <div class="stats-row">
        <div class="si">
            <div class="sn" data-stat="2">0</div>
            <div class="sl" data-i18n="stat1_label">Años<br>programando</div>
        </div>
        <div class="si">
            <div class="sn">∞</div>
            <div class="sl" data-i18n="stat2_label">Cafés<br>consumidos</div>
        </div>
        <div class="si">
            <div class="sn" data-stat="1">0</div>
            <div class="sl" data-i18n="stat3_label">Easter egg<br>encontrado</div>
        </div>
        <div class="si">
            <div class="sn" data-stat="100" data-suffix="%">0</div>
